First of all, thanks Pamona!
@rodella, it really is not a good idea to post serial numbers in the comments, when they are already included in the torrent, as this often causes the S/Ns to be blacklisted...

Anyone having trouble registering this in Snow Leopard (Prefs win appears, but with no Divx pref pane visible) - go to /Library/PreferencePanes/DivX.prefPane and double-click it.  It will tell you that the PreferencePane already exists - re-install it.  Relaunch DivX player, select Extras -> DivX For Mac Registration.  This time Preferences will appear, with a message 'to use the DivX PreferencePane, preferences must quit and relaunch' - click OK, double-click the (now visible) DivX prefs, and complete your registration...(roll of drums, followed by Cymbal crash ;-)
